OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FSmall business owners in the West
OL,8,FCountry have warned the Government's
OL,9,FAutumn Budget will "hit hard," with
OL,10,Fone saying they're even considering
OL,11,Fmoving their company abroad.
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced a
OL,14,Fhost of measures designed to raise
OL,15,F#40bn as part of her Budget in
OL,16,FParliament on Wednesday, 30 October
OL,17,F2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/18
