OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FAmong these measures are a rise in the
OL,8,Fnational minimum wage and a hike to
OL,9,Femployers' National Insurance
OL,10,FContributions (NICs), a form of income
OL,11,Ftax.
OL,13,FBut small businesses have warned -
OL,14,Fbefore and since these announcements -
OL,15,Fthat these policies will force some
OL,16,Fbusinesses to close and could lead to
OL,17,Fstaff being let go.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/18
