OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FAfter hearing the news about dual
OL,8,Frising costs of NICs and the minimum
OL,9,Fwage, Krishna Chand, who runs a family-
OL,10,Frun food company in Bristol, said that
OL,11,Fin the future "if I need 12 staff, I
OL,12,Fwill go for ten".
OL,14,FHe said: "We live a tight life
OL,15,Factually because of what's going on
OL,16,Fwith the Budget. Customers are
OL,17,Fspending less, and as a business, we
OL,18,Fneed more money to run our business.
OL,19,FSo this is having an impact on
OL,20,Freducing staff.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/18
