OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FHe also fears that the changes will
OL,8,Fsee more small businesses struggle to
OL,9,Fstay open - and he is even thinking
OL,10,Fabout moving his company abroad.
OL,12,FKrishna said: "Because they're
OL,13,Fincreasing the minimum wage and
OL,14,Fincreasing the National Insurance
OL,15,F(Contributions), it's going to have an
OL,16,Fimpact on everyone. Lots of businesses
OL,17,Fare closing down.
