OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"We as a family business are also
OL,8,Flooking to relocate just because of
OL,9,Fwhat's going on in this country. We
OL,10,Fare not sure we are going to be here
OL,11,Ffor five, seven years. We don't want
OL,12,Fto live here, unfortunately.
OL,14,F"The life is not what it used to be
OL,15,Fbefore. Now, we have to spend more
OL,16,Ftime in the business just to sustain
OL,17,Fthe profit and to keep other staff
OL,18,Fhappy, and to pay the wages on time".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/18
