OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FAsked if the Budget has encouraged him
OL,8,Fto take his family business abroad, he
OL,9,Freplied: "110%".
OL,11,F"The government has to really consider
OL,12,Fthe small businesses," he continued.
OL,13,F"They should not look at only the
OL,14,Fpeople who are under-earning as
OL,15,Femployees, they should also look at
OL,16,Fthe people running the businesses who
OL,17,Fare also under-earning. They should
OL,18,Fhelp them, they should support them".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/18
