OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FGreen Party co-leader and Bristol
OL,8,FCentral MP, Carla Denyer, says the
OL,9,FBudget will impact people on 'lower
OL,10,Fand middle incomes' who own businesses
OL,12,FUnlike many small business owners,
OL,13,FKrishna said he does "not blame
OL,14,FLabour".
OL,16,FHe said: "Yes, it is going to have a
OL,17,Fhard hit, but the people preparing the
OL,18,FBudget have the best interest for the
OL,19,Fcountry, for the businesses and for
OL,20,Fthe people who employ people".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/18
