OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FPeter Eastwood, who founded and runs a
OL,8,Fsoft furnishings company in Berkley,
OL,9,FGloucestershire, is also now "taking
OL,10,Fstock" of the Budget, and has concerns
OL,11,Fabout the future.
OL,13,F"It's quite a concern - I think we
OL,14,Fwere expecting some bad news," he said.
OL,16,F"We've gone from two people to 17
OL,17,Fpeople in a couple of years, and we're
OL,18,Fgoing to put that on hold, I think,
OL,19,Ffor a while. So, that's a big concern
OL,20,Ffor us, what it means for us over the
OL,21,Fnext three, four, five years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/18
