OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"We've got a lot of staff and the
OL,8,Fbiggest thing we have to do every
OL,9,Fmonth is pay them. And that's the
OL,10,Fbiggest concern we have. We support
OL,11,Fpay rises but we've got to be able to
OL,12,Fafford them and at the moment, we're
OL,13,Fjust very nervous about all the extra
OL,14,Fthat we're finding coming at us."
OL,16,FHe told ITV West Country that he feels
OL,17,F"apprehensive" and "targeted" by the
OL,18,FGovernment's Budget.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/18
