OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"It's the accumulation of things over
OL,8,Fthe last four or five years and I
OL,9,Fthink there has been a lot of
OL,10,Fincreases on small businesses for a
OL,11,Flong time and that hurts," he said.
OL,13,F"Small businesses, in the round,
OL,14,Fgenerally pay huge amounts of tax and
OL,15,Fdon't avoid it," he said. "They lump
OL,16,Fus together as if we're all fat cats
OL,17,Fand that's not the case in business.
OL,18,FMost people are working their socks
OL,19,Foff".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/18
