OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FPeter said he would like to see more
OL,8,Fpeople with experience running small
OL,9,Fbusinesses in Government, adding he
OL,10,Fbelieves "small businesses are the
OL,11,Fbackbone of this country".
OL,13,FNicola Wheeler, from Exeter Business
OL,14,FImprovement District (BID), also fears
OL,15,Fthat the minimum wage hike will cost
OL,16,Fjobs and could even lead to some
OL,17,Fbusinesses closing down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/18
