OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FShe said: "Whilst we completely
OL,8,Funderstand and agree with the right to
OL,9,Fprotect workers, in actual fact, I am
OL,10,Fworried that in the long-term we will
OL,11,Fsee that employers are unable to
OL,12,Fcreate jobs, they are going to be
OL,13,Fpotentially making people redundant
OL,14,Fand, in the long-term, potentially,
OL,15,Fbusinesses will be having to make
OL,16,Fdifficult decisions about whether or
OL,17,Fnot they can continue to operate".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/18
