OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FTorbay's Liberal Democrat MP Steve
OL,8,FDarling says the issue of crumbling
OL,9,Fhospital estates in the South West is
OL,10,Fbeing 'kicked into the long grass' by
OL,11,FLabour, while the hit to small
OL,12,Fbusinesses could 'hold back growth'
OL,14,FSimon Thompson, the owner of a cafe in
OL,15,FNewquay, added that he has been left
OL,16,F"very worried" by the Chancellor's
OL,17,FBudget and said changes to NICs have
OL,18,Fadded a nine per cent increase to his
OL,19,Fbill.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/18
