OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"The real surprise to me is they've
OL,8,Falso lowered the rate at which I start
OL,9,Fpaying National Insurance, so that
OL,10,Fwill be a big jump for me.
OL,12,F"And then with minimum wage going up,
OL,13,Fthat's marvellous for the people I
OL,14,Femploy, I am happy for them. But the
OL,15,Fconstraints that puts on me as a
OL,16,Fbusiness owner, with rising costs of
OL,17,Fproduction, electricity, wages, tax.
OL,18,FThe questions I will be asking myself
OL,19,Fover this winter will be 'can we
OL,20,Fsustain that as a business?'"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/18
