OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FBut not every small business owner is
OL,8,Fconcerned - some can see the positives.
OL,10,FMatthew Cousins, the owner of a
OL,11,Fscaffolding company in Exeter that
OL,12,Femploys around fifty people, fears the
OL,13,Fhike in NICs will cost the company
OL,14,Ftens of thousands of pounds. But he
OL,15,Fadmits that "now at least the
OL,16,Funcertainty is over".
OL,18,FMatthew is also board director of the
OL,19,Fcity's Chamber of Commerce.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/18
