OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FHe said: "A lot of the Chamber members
OL,8,Fhave been saying that they don't know
OL,9,Fwhat has been happening, and what is
OL,10,Fgoing to happen and at least now they
OL,11,Fdo and can plan for it," he added.
OL,13,F'They are not for the people, they are
OL,14,Fall for themselves' - How people are
OL,15,Freacting to the Budget
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/18
