OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"I am sure they are trying to do their
OL,8,Fbest", one person in Exeter told ITV
OL,9,FNews West Country. "Everybody wanted a
OL,10,Fchange, I am not sure they are going
OL,11,Fin the right direction but only time
OL,12,Fwill tell."
OL,14,FAnother person in the city said
OL,15,Fraising the cap on bus fares by 50%,
OL,16,Ffrom #2 to #3, will have a "big
OL,17,Feffect".
OL,19,F"My son and daughter work in town and
OL,20,Fthey will be paying the extra, without
OL,21,Freally any wage increases", they added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/18
