OL,3,C'It's going to hit hard': Business
OL,4,Cowners warn of job cuts following the
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FMeanwhile, a third person said they
OL,8,Fthink it's "absolutely disgusting what
OL,9,F(the Government) are doing".
OL,11,F"They are not for the people, are
OL,12,Fthey? And they're not for the working
OL,13,Fclass either. They are all for
OL,14,Fthemselves," they said.
